{"tid":439700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：壯大愛國愛港力量","createTime":"2017-10-18T05:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:20:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"493955f705b34a5dddf6216bfda6729768994d73","tid":439700,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171018/s00001/ca434ce0e5be7fa7628948873e9d8632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171018%2Fs00001%2Fca434ce0e5be7fa7628948873e9d8632.jpg&h=e18d722d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平在今早十九大開幕大會上作報告稱，香港、澳門回歸祖國以來，「一國兩制」實踐取得舉世公認的成功。他表示，保持香港、澳門長期繁榮穩定，必須全面準確貫徹「一國兩制」、「港人治港」、「澳人治澳」、「高度自治」的方針，嚴格依照憲法和基本法辦事，完善與基本法實施相關的制度和機制。<br />\n<br />\n習近平重申，要支持特別行政區政府和行政長官依法施政、積極作為，團結帶領香港、澳門各界人士齊心協力謀發展、促和諧，保障和改善民生，有序推進民主，維護社會穩定，履行維護國家主權、安全、發展利益的憲制責任。<br />\n<br />\n習近平還提到大灣區建設和泛珠三角區域合作，稱支持香港、澳門融入國家發展大局，全面推進內地同香港、澳門互利合作，制定完善便利香港、澳門居民在內地發展的政策措施。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，堅持愛國者為主體的「港人治港」、「澳人治澳」，要發展壯大愛國愛港愛澳力量，增強香港、澳門同胞的國家意識和愛國精神，「讓香港、澳門同胞同祖國人民共擔民族復興的歷史責任、共享祖國繁榮富強的偉大榮光。」<br />\n<br />\n他最後稱，只要包括港澳台同胞在內的全體中華兒女順應歷史大勢、共擔民族大義，就一定能夠共創中華民族偉大復興的美好未來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171018/s00001/1508302372114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171018%2Fs00001%2F1508302372114&d=bdQJtR5Xuplh%2BIUX7YPb1UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8a9f78b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171018%2Fs00001%2F1508302372114&h=82176ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171018/s00001/1508302372114</a>"},{"pid":"1364c1d5e10d0c450a0be33bc8c81464abb88014","tid":439700,"uid":37735,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"無人想同你搞咩民族復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9fb8b4e9ea8c546db475d5fbd851f738550839","tid":439700,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"哇<br />\n制造大量長者有野做"},{"pid":"f226c488168b7fc517f767df816dbda8b61e2ceb","tid":439700,"uid":38523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"咪即係x社會？"},{"pid":"ced631d594607c31069ceb949dd7bd0d61e36443","tid":439700,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:10:47.000Z","msg":"愛字頭有糧出"},{"pid":"46a8db757ce142932f37d5a19d874c67d52fdd17","tid":439700,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:11:01.000Z","msg":"愛港力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325cdc2a6f72cae8005fd2246a2b77d2aed65868","tid":439700,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:12:48.000Z","msg":"愛字頭發達LA"},{"pid":"16cab3fc97d97de3cad908fdd076aa668375fee9","tid":439700,"uid":3117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛字頭有糧出</blockquote><br />\n不嬲都有 不過睇黎勢力會愈來愈大"},{"pid":"b4c89a0fc502249a02fb741ddc75c755c7b4a8da","tid":439700,"uid":36178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"最尾果句衰撚過比人咒絕子絕孫"},{"pid":"504e6c2aee378f94b7b5051886bc2d6e8aca69ec","tid":439700,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"不如坦白啲攪文革啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf231ba407078a0d675dd42ac1f7ff87ce8d902e","tid":439700,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:15:42.000Z","msg":"揸美國護照嘅中共領導人果然唔同啲"},{"pid":"d5bbbf54d344618f50a341e4640bf996cf8005ec","tid":439700,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:16:43.000Z","msg":"佢個女喺邊話"},{"pid":"b3da4223e5601c027b0bf7ee0b71f67399214fe